                       ScopedTypeVariables, LambdaCase, NamedFieldPuns,
                       DeriveGeneric, DeriveDataTypeable,
                       DataKinds, RankNTypes, OverloadedLabels, TemplateHaskell, QuasiQuotes,
                       TypeFamilies, GeneralizedNewtypeDeriving, StandaloneDeriving, TupleSections,
                       RecordWildCards, TypeOperators, NoMonomorphismRestriction, PatternSynonyms, NoImplicitPrelude
